Prompt 2.2.1: Create Base Layout
Objective: Build the foundational layout components.
Instructions for AI Agent:

Create the base layout components with a clean, minimal design:

1. src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro:
   - Accept props: title (string), description (string)
   - Include HTML head with meta tags
   - Include global CSS
   - Load branding config and apply CSS variables for colors
   - Include Header and Footer components
   - Provide a slot for page content
   - Structure:

   <html>
   <head>
     <title>{title}</title>
     <meta description={description} />
     <!-- Apply branding colors as CSS variables -->
   </head>
   <body>
     <Header />
     <main>
       <slot />
     </main>
     <Footer />
   </body>
 </html>

 2. src/components/layout/Header.astro:
   - Logo (left side) - use branding config
   - Site name (next to logo) - use branding config
   - Search bar (center) - basic input, non-functional for now
   - User menu (right side) - Login/Register buttons for now
   - Minimal styling with Tailwind
   - Sticky header that stays at top on scroll
   - Height: ~64px

3. src/components/layout/Footer.astro:
   - Simple footer with:
     - Copyright notice
     - Links: About, Terms, Privacy, Contact
     - Social media icons (placeholder)
   - Background: light gray
   - Padding: 2rem vertical

4. src/components/layout/Sidebar.astro:
   - Accept props: categories (Category[])
   - Display list of categories
   - Each category is a clickable link (use # for now)
   - Show video count next to each category
   - Styling:
     - Fixed width: 240px
     - Light background
     - Padding: 1rem
     - Rounded corners for active/hover states

Design principles:
- Clean and minimal (like early YouTube)
- Lots of white space
- Clear typography hierarchy
- Subtle shadows and borders
- Responsive (mobile-first)

